{"tid":749514,"cid":15,"subCid":0,"title":"金融海嘯時出售賣權，巴菲特狂撈 24 億美元","createTime":"2018-07-20T05:48:45.000Z","updateTime":"2018-07-22T05:24:50.000Z","uid":28765,"like":5,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":17,"replies":[{"pid":"c0f551b08f953bb2adebf7f4a7b04d5b152e8e3e","tid":749514,"uid":28765,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-07-20T05:48:45.000Z","msg":"股神巴菲特曾經砲轟衍生性商品是「金融業的大規模毀滅性武器」（financial weapons of mass destruction），不過巴菲特心口不一，玩衍生性商品一把罩。2008 年全球金融海嘯之際，股神大舉出售賣權（put），他旗下的波克夏海瑟威（Berkshire Hathaway）為此賺進 24 億美元。<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"http://img.technews.tw/wp-content/uploads/2018/01/05150055/shutterstock_353934110-624x478.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=http%3A%2F%2Fimg.technews.tw%2Fwp-content%2Fuploads%2F2018%2F01%2F05150055%2Fshutterstock_353934110-624x478.jpg&h=eecb3c72&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n<br />\nZeroHedge 9 日引述外媒報導，波克夏海瑟威在 2004~2008 年出售大批股市指數賣權，如今這些賣權逐漸到期，首批在今年 6 月，最後一批將在 2026 年 1 月到期。這些賣權綁定全球四大股市指數，估計 2008~2017 年間共為波克夏海瑟威賺進 24 億美元。<br />\n<br />\nYahoo Finance 解釋，賣權給予持有者下行保障。持有賣權的人，有權利在特定日期以約定好的價格，向賣方賣出標的物。以這個例子來說，擔心股市下跌的一方，支付權利金敲進賣權以獲得保障。出售賣權的一方（巴菲特）看好股市將漲，出售賣權賺取權利金。<br />\n<br />\n波克夏海瑟威的賣權是歐式選擇權，期滿才能要求履約。股神眼光精準，2008 年底以來，標普 500 指數大漲將近 3 倍，英國 FTSE 10 指數也飆高 70% 以上。股市大漲使得選擇權沒有履約價值，大筆權利金落入股神口袋。芝加哥選擇權交易所（CBOE）Options Institute 主管 Russell Rhoads 表示，股市持續飆高，波克夏海瑟威可賺進銀子，未來應該仍會有好表現。<br />\n<br />\n（本文由 MoneyDJ新聞 授權轉載；首圖來源：shutterstock）<br />\n<br />\n原來巴菲特D SP做成廿年咁耐<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 邊到買到佢個歐式期權"},{"pid":"fdbc5283d8e0db23a5925a1e574b319bef754921","tid":749514,"uid":28765,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-07-20T05:49:05.000Z","msg":"<a href=\"http://finance.technews.tw/2018/07/10/financial-crisis-buffett-put/\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=http%3A%2F%2Ffinance.technews.tw%2F2018%2F07%2F10%2Ffinancial-crisis-buffett-put%2F&d=R6lfK%2BfGLgT%2FMB3V0C5%2FP%2F755KD0hvcRsprRlRVhNBc%3D&h=12c4eef7\" target=\"_blank\">http://finance.technews.tw/2018/07/10/financial-crisis-buffett-put/</a>"},{"pid":"5a005b8cd14b0319acf03e98a9e50e0027e44f7f","tid":749514,"uid":77355,"like":1,"dislike":3,"score":-2,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-07-21T04:03:45.000Z","msg":"將牛熊由投機變投資<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/oh.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"00e06237a51deb23a61d2ecb0775be378e743ce3","tid":749514,"uid":36143,"like":8,"dislike":0,"score":8,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-07-21T04:15:49.000Z","msg":"二十年short put<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n玩港股既話兩個月已經要係咁補倉call margin<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"501fb3908f70623f790bdf4b5b3cb6519a5490e1","tid":749514,"uid":33263,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-07-21T07:32:14.000Z","msg":"你個本要好大<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 先做到"},{"pid":"f1c269ab389db0c9b623c2c5105d3b28d5d91e54","tid":749514,"uid":39508,"like":7,"dislike":0,"score":7,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-07-21T07:53:06.000Z","msg":"佢有資本好難輸喎<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n差唔多到期用錢谷高個市又袋袋平安<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />  <br />\n同賭仔永遠贏唔到錢道理一樣"},{"pid":"e6bdf2219f3d2db397ad2054cf331e4663c0fe04","tid":749514,"uid":125976,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-07-21T07:54:52.000Z","msg":"SP 咁長按金好貴<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/donno.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"df839157af298a307b2476ea44412348aba78520","tid":749514,"uid":46933,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"e6bdf2219f3d2db397ad2054cf331e4663c0fe04","tid":749514,"uid":125976,"like":1,"disli